data.description: This spacious 5 bedroom, 3 bathroom single-family home is located in the Wedgefield Park neighborhood of Norfolk, VA. The renovated kitchen with stainless steel appliances, butcher block countertops, and a breakfast bar is perfect for entertaining guests or cooking up a storm for your family. The primary suite has been renovated and features a walk-in closet and private bathroom, so you can relax and unwind after a long day. The large backyard is perfect for entertaining guests, playing games, or just enjoying the fresh air. The sunroom is the perfect place to read a book or take a nap. Schools, shopping, and parks are all nearby, making this the perfect place to raise a family. Living near the Ingleside Road Station provides easy access to the Tide, making it a breeze to reach the heart of downtown Norfolk, including City Hall, MacArthur Mall, Blocker YMCA, Sentara Norfolk General Hospital, and CHKD. Pilgrim ThermoPak oil heat installed Aug 2005.
